subject: Golf
lead_paragraph: Annika Sorenstam shot a three-over-par 75, hurting her chances of ending her career by winning the Dubai Ladies Masters for a third straight time. Sorenstam had four bogeys and one birdie, falling four shots behind the leader, Anja Monke of Germany.
